[normal]Why do numbers of women in STEM academic careers decline further up the career ladder?
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]When women leave academia, what careers do they transition into? What are the consequences of scientif
[normal]ically trained women applying their skills in different employment sectors?
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;[bold]What should universities and the higher education sector do to
[normal] retain women graduates and PhD students in academic careers? Are there examples of good practice?
[normal]What role should the Government have in encouraging the retention of women in academic STEM careers? 
